    <h2>Temperature</h2>
    <p>A <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Temperature" target="_blank">temperature</a> expresses hot and cold, as measured with a thermometer. </p>
    <p>There are various temperature scales. The most commonly used scales are the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Celsius" target="_blank">Celsius</a> scale  (denoted °C), <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fahrenheit" target="_blank">Fahrenheit</a> scale (denoted °F), and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kelvin" target="_blank">Kelvin</a> scale (denoted K).</p>
